reviews.review_text: 1st McDonalds in Burnaby B.C. that made my brother and myself wish we tried this location earlier. The food was not as greasy like back at home, and had flavor. Definitely going back to this location when Im down there again.

Just went through this mcdonalds drivethru yeesterday. I ordered the quarter pounder meal and honestly it was one of the best once ive ever tasted for a long time now. It was fresh like it was just made also the fries was hot and fresh. Surrey mcdonalds should learn to make fresh sandwiches and fries also. When i buy the quarter pounder meal in  all the surrey mcdonalds locations its never fresh and the meat always tastes so gross. The fries is never fresh there either. Plsss learn from this example surrey mcdonalds locations. Way to go guysssss i enjoyeddddddd the quarter pounder and fries soo much def will come back again. Even the drive thru line up was long but it was sooo worth the wait.
It was great experience as Jaspreet (Team leader) served me and I had great customer experience. Even the food was above the average so definitely going to visit again.
Very good service and food. Like the place. Very quick service

These 5 stars are ONLY for the young South Asian woman manning the drive thru tonight. She was getting abuse hurled at her from waiting customers, I think they were having machine issues, etc. She was very patient and I feel REALLY bad for her. I have noticed this is the only mcdonalds that seems perpetually understaffed. Thats always a management, upper management issue. Make it a place that people WANT to work at so your employees dont get abuse hurled at them.

Had a really good customer service experience with Derek at the drive through this morning. He helped us navigate a misunderstanding that we had with a coupon bundle. He wound up optimizing our purchase with a combination of coupons, which we really appreciated!
Derek is amazing... hands down the absolute best drive thru experience I have ever had in my entire life... I am glad I came to this McDonalds today... almost stopped at the last one... Yay Derek!!!

I ordered skip with this location and when I got my food they left a note and a complementary donut. The not said thank you and they were very appreciative of our order. I was very shocked as this is a high chain company. Very satisfied with this McDonald s location.
Going through the drive thru made our day,the guy that took the order sounded like a professional radio announcer with a great sense of humor

The manager at this location ( I didnt get his name but he had long bangs) was super nice and friendly! I had enough points for a Mcflurry and wanted the shamrock one which was not available in their system but he so kindly got it for me! He was very professional and I had just had s horrible experience with the manager at rbc so I was really grateful for this experience, and made my day! He was wayyyyyy better than the rbc manager named olimpia malsegna she was absolutely rude and disrespectful...
Order taken and filled for 2, very quickly
It was ok but this location doesnt have good seating at all besides the booths.  And it smelled   like pee.
Lady at the drive thru gave exceptional service
Gave me a cookie, a hand written thank you note, and a large fries. Very friendly and great service.
Derek at the drive thru window always makes my day everytime I see him. He is the most upbeat, positive, kind soul that I have ever met working for McDonalds. Its always a pleasure!

Its McDonalds... Consistent and feel this one put their food together most consistent. Order happy meal several time  and notice the fries are not as salty compared to regular order. This is a huge plus compare to other McDonalds Ive been to.
Its McDonalds. This one was relatively clean and food was fine.
They are understaffed during morning peak hours. Schedule more staff management ! Poor employers working their neck off, they deserve better. The 5 stars is for the employers only

This McDonald is open late, has good staffing and a large parking lot! Drive through has always been smooth. If your order needs more time they ask you to park in the lot and they will bring it out to you. Its across the street from a Burger King and Cora. Me and Eds is on the same block. Just outside the busy area of Highgate shopping plaza. Lots of food delivery companies pick up from here.

Today I went to Drive-thru and there was a girl named Dupinder. She was very kind to me. I had facing a problem while using the mobile app and I asked her to help me. She literally gave me her time even she was busy. I really like her service and also want to thankyou Macdonald to hire such a nice girl.

Ok. After reviewing McDonald s Newton, I thought of giving the Edmonds Location a 5 star! We always go here for drive-thru or dine-in. They always get everything right,  cashiers are friendly, food is fresh. They have high customer service standards here. The store inside is always well-kept and no dirty tables lying around compared to Newton. I do not expect much with McDonald s restaurant nowadays but this one, so far so good. (Compared to Newton in Surrey, the worst Mcdonald s I have ever visited lol)
I love to come here!

Awesome I love the way the workers treat to the customers I haven t been in morning but the night shift staff is so good I can t stop my hands to give 5 stars ratings just beacuse of their hard work and way of talking to customers night staff is really doing job appreciated.

I generally wouldnt write a review for McDonalds but I was thoroughly impressed by the service by one of their employees at the Edmonds location. The 2 cheeseburger meal was removed from the menu a long time ago so Ive been ordering a cheeseburger, fries, coke separately all these years. The server saved me a couple dollars by turning it into a double cheeseburger meal!

A decaf coffee served hot will always get 5 stars. Caucasian gentleman taking the orders on the weekday mornings is always cheerful. Very enthusiastic and friendly. He should assume a manager position but its always nice seeing someone that cheerful during groggy morning drive thrus.
Everyday I must have a cup of coffee I am so Interested Mc Coffee Thank You so much for all team Service very good

Despite the pleothra of negative reviews this particular outlet seems to be getting from everyone, I have always had positive experiences with this place. I have visited multiple times and never have they messed up my orders. The only issue I found was that they were always running low on toys that are typically included with the Happy Meals. But the suggestion for this issue (according to them) is to keep whatever they give (like childrens books) and to return it the next time for a toy. I have never tried exchanging the books for the toys so I do not know how that works.
Service Changes due to Covid but still nice to dine in for your daily breakfast
Went here for breakfast Sep. 3 2018. Food was perfect. Hash browns were beyond good, having perfect crispyness and flavor, while sandwiches were neatly put together. Order was accurate 100%

As you would expect in most McDonalds, it is busy.  I do like the drive thru though.  Sometimes you may chat with one of employees, particularly one in the morning, if you regularly come here through a drive thru.  He is a nice chatty one.

I do not often this location, but my five star review comes from the fact that this was my childhood restaurant. I remember when it was a small squareish building with dated decor and no drive through. We didnt have much growing up so the best treat would be a hashbrown. Ive had too many good experiences here to outweigh the bad ones (which are few and far between)

Ok so heres the deal. This is our regular McDonalds. We often get breakfast there on the way out of town. Its always below average. Today our drive through breakfast was SUPER. Everything was hot and tasty and hash browns were crispy and not greasy as usual. We were there at 10:15am Saturday 26th May. And its was busy! I wish this was our experience every time :)
Nice staff and its always super busy here.  I once saw about 30 orders and they were really quick. No fancy seats here so you wont be staying here for long
Great service, really appreciate it!
Very fast service. Food is somewhat above average McDonalds quality.
Good branch. Good staff. Fast service.

My wife and I love Mcds coffee and there is a coffee reward program. Our millennial kids love Starbucks. But everyone in the family likes Mcds sausage egg McMuffin. So a couple times a month or was it 4 times last month.Haha! Ample parking and we have even walked over from the Higate steet level parkade to grab a coffee on the way home,after shopping at Higate.

Derek in the drive thru is the best person. I saw him serving us these years and I am very happy from his service.   He is the best person in the highgate location.  He is very nice and polite. Sincerely Khalida
Quick and they got my order right. Something it seems most mcdonalds locations lately can never do. But they did it.

The McDonalds here on Kingsway & 1block east of Salisbury & Kingsway has a drive through, a outside to be not disturbed, a fire place that runs 24/7...365 p) year...a very friendly staff who if they make a mistake they will correct it the next day!!! Just keep ur receipt...there will be no questions asked & will put together quietly & promply!!! They take care of their customers as soon as possible!!! Money is not the only thing they think...they ask how ur doing...enjoy a quiet, cooled building that offers u breakfast all day...dont forget ur coupons that 1 gets every 6 weeks...put those coupons in ur purses & wallets...itll be here quicker than u think...have a good thirst quenshing coke!!! Have fun...make sure you know what coupons to bring for y & ur partner..., enjoy....
Always fresh coffee and so glad it s drive thru because it s much easier when you re always on the go or have your kids in the car!!

ordered tyler 1 special here but told me they dont know what it is. but this one worker ashley hooks me up with tyler 1 special: 11/10 2 McDoubles without onions a jr chicken medium fries 2 apple pies and an Oreo McFlurry
Excellent service.All staff is so friendly and helpful
I was in the area so I stopped in , its not a favorite   took forever to place my order and have it completed   Ill skip it next time and go to a different McDonalds
Great service! We ordered dinner today and the food was tasty, clean and organized. Thanks for being there for us during these difficult times!
FINALLY, A MCDS THAT LISTENS, AND GETS YOUR ORDER DONE RIGHT, THE VERY FIRST TIME. BRAVO ME&EDS MCDS, BRAVO. PS, WHERES MARVIN AT??? BRING BACK THE MARV!!! WE WANT THE MARV!!! .
Usually fast drive through is a better choice for those who urged for work or school, and it is fast service.
I liked this McDonaldss it is nice and close to my location. The staff is always friendly and organized!
Service was fast and friendly. Drive-thru access was good. Food was...McDonalds...
Got my usual order, but the best part is the staff on this branch are really thoughtful and attentive.  Thanks for the extra mayo.
I always come here every morning only coz of Derek such a wonderful person he has best customer service and such a wonderful person with good behaviour I will give him 5 start
Great service. Friendly workers and most importantly their ice cream machine works
you can expect the same food same taste same quality everytime you visit any one of the mcdonalds. Staff is always friendly and courteous.
Limited seat and parking!
Efficient and systematic service.
They messed up my order twice, but there is a manager called Ryan who made it up for me. Great guy and excellent service.
Sometimes takes 10-15mins from the moment I advise im at the curbside pickup..sometimes 5mins.  All depends how busy they there.
Service was quick, dine in is open, curbside pickup is open. You can order at counter or order on inhouse kiosk.
The hot chocolate I got was really good. Usually it s really watered down, but today it had just the right amount of chocolate.
One of the best stuff in this location is Derek best customer service and every morning when I come here he made my day
Friendly staff,fast service and cleanliness
Great people even though the ice cream machine didnt work still had a good experience
I hurt my back helping someone push their broken down car out of the drive thru. Good food though
Totally recommend  ,  delicious sandwiches and coffe
Its mcdonalds what else do you need to know
Ngl they took 20 minutes to get my order and they still messed it up. Not very happy about that
Good environment Good service
Always fast both in the drivethru and inside. Staff is always friendly.
I ordered incorrectly  staff fixed it for me and gave me refund for difference
Much developed by taste compared to last year the same time! My taste has changed? Maybe!
Very reliable and on time service, i highly recommend. They have a great parking lot for customers
Other than not honoring a coupon, I have never really had any issues at this McDonalds
Good service. Inexpensive food and friendly staff.
They are perfect
The burgers here are delicious. Especially the mighty angus burger. They have new one called jalapeno guacamole angus burger.
Great place awesome staff. I go here alot its good food.
Best and freshest egg McMuffin Ive ever had at any mcd before
Amazing Quality Of Information On Stores & Services, & Places Too Stop In All Around Good App Thus Far.
This location is great. Food is always hot and fresh
i love this place because they make really good food and really good cheeseburgers
I have to say this place it keeps the standard very well. They even remember the details of what I usually order.
I go here all the time and always happy
This is a good McDonalds.  The staff is very efficient and friendly
Amazing staff and fast and effective even in the early hours of the day, got me on my way. Thanks
24/7 , good food , never really been disappointed
Quick service, clean place, nice ambience. Go for it.
Nice place. Good place to ear with children. Good for short visits.  I visit regularly.
Love McDs for seductive sin food! Yes, I actually love McDs!!!
Same tastes as other McDonalds, staff are nicer here
Its a McDonalds. Can get good food we can get that food its up to me
Quick drive thru service. Love the food
It was McDonalds, pretty standardized service. Quality was good.
Super good  and always helpful in hunger Crisis
Like this mc Donalds ,the younger staff are great here .
Great! The food is good and its clean!
Quick service and got everything we asked for
Great, well-priced food.
Best location in Burnaby. Always fresh and delicious.
Its McDonalds... I mean if you like McDonalds its good. Otherwise no.
Faster and as usual delicious Big Mac combo
